== Rama ==

Ram  Vixnnuchea dha ovtarantlo satvo ovtar. Ikxvaku kullantlo iodhyecho raza Doxroth ani patt'ttoranni Kouslea hancho put. Obheasokanchea motan tacho kall i.so. adim 2000 te 1950.  Tachi zolmotith choitr xu. nom' (ramonm') Valomiki munichea "Ramainn" hea mhakaveant to adorx put, ekoptnivorti, mhaprakromi, sorvoxrextth zhuzari ani adorx rajio oxem Ramachem vornnon kelam. Nardan tachevixim vornnon kelam tem oxem- ikxvaku kullantlo ram' ho adorx pururx, sobit mukhamoll, vixal kopol, vhodd dolle, purai kuddicher agllich kanti axil'lo, vidhiet khampo, rajnitigone, sojzonacho songroh ani durzonacho nigroh korpi, dhorm', orth ani kam' hea tinui puruxarthanchem iogio toren sevon korpi, songit, vade, chitrkola hatunt huxar, projahitokxod ani projnonank prio osom ho Ram xrextth purux. Raza Doxorthak Kouslea,  Sumitra ani Koiko-i oxo tin Ranneo axil'leo. Tankam boroch temp bhurgim zali na. Tannem rixioxrring muni vorvim putrokamextthi yogn kelo. Tedna Kouslieger Ram, Sumitrager Lokxmonn ani Xotrud'n ani Koikeyiger Bhorot oxe char put zale. Soglle put gineannani,  gunni ani huxar axil'le. Ram ho hoteacher ani ghoddeacher bospant ani rothsoncholon korpant fixal axil'lo.  To pondra vorsancho astona aple iogonebhuimek rakxosamposun rakhonn mellchi dekhun vixrvomitr Rixi taka gheun gelo. Thoim tannem Ramak bola ani otibla heo zhuzvidea xikoileo. Tea vellar Raman, Tattoka he Rakxoxinnik jivexim marli. Toxench marich, subahu adi rakxosank dhanvddavn ghale. Tedana vixvamitran khoxi zavn Ramak divio ostram dilim. Uprant Vixrvamitran taka mithilek zonok razager vholo. Vattent Raman goutom Rixichi bail ohilea hika xapmukt keli.

